title: Hikikomori Pilgrimage

subTitle: Hourly news updates featuring current affairs, business news, financial updates and global weather forecasts.

title: Stories From Kobe's Western Cuisine

subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of programmes that highlights Japan through its wildlife, landscapes, art, technology, lifestyle, food and communities is presented.

title: Dining with the Chef Mini
subTitle: The techniques, ingredients and harmony of Japanese food recipes in just five minutes. Chef Rika cooks alongside master chef Tatsuo Saito to show viewers how to prepare delicious Japanese dishes at home.

title: Sumopedia
subTitle: A look at the material and story behind yukata, a form of clothing usually worn by sumo wrestlers during summer.

title: NHK Newsline
subTitle: Hourly news updates featuring current affairs, business news, financial updates and global weather forecasts.

title: Dining with the Chef
subTitle: Cook Japanese dishes using canned tuna! Chef Saito shows you a warm rice bowl topped with tuna, fried tofu and egg, plus a refreshing tuna salad enhanced with the aroma of yuzu.

title: Newsroom Tokyo
subTitle: Comprehensive coverage of events in Japan and Asia. It explains the day's developments and what is behind them.

title: Direct Talk
subTitle: Mizushiri Yoriko won the Silver Bear in the short film competition at the 2025 Berlin International Film Festival. She talks about her passion for creating animations that evoke a sense of touch.
